                The first step involves a crucial interaction between parents
                and teachers. You can either click the Enquire Now button on our
                website to send us your inquiry, or call us at <a href="tel:9900077180" class="text-primary text-decoration-line: underline"> +91 9900077180 </a> or <a href="tel:9900077181" class="text-primary text-decoration-line: underline">+91 9900077181 </a> to
                arrange a visit in person. This will help us establish the
                foundation for your child's educational journey with us.
              </Text>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row gap-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <Text type="subtitle" class="text-[#1C1C1C]/50">STEP</Text>
              <Text type="h2" class="font-sans font-bold">02</Text>
            </div>
            <div>
              <Text type="h2" class="max-md:text-[22px]">
                Online <span>Application Form</span>
              </Text>
              <div class="p-3 max-md:p-1"></div>
              <Text type="base">
                During your visit to the school, you can obtain the brochure and
                application form for Rs. 1500/- (Non-Refundable) through cash,
                cheque, or DD payable to Ekam School, Bengaluru.
              </Text>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row gap-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <Text type="subtitle" class="text-[#1C1C1C]/50">STEP</Text>
              <Text type="h2" class="font-sans font-bold">03</Text>
            </div>
            <div>
              <Text type="h2" class="max-md:text-[22px]">
                Entrance <span> Exam</span>
              </Text>
              <div class="p-3 max-md:p-1"></div>
              <Text type="base">
                After submitting the application form at the school campus, your child will take an entrance exam that covers essential subjects and languages. The answer sheets will be reviewed by the principal and program heads. We will then notify you of the exam results and your child's clearance status.
              </Text>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row gap-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
