                    A certified copy of the Caste Certificate (if the student
                    belongs to SC/ST/BC).
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    Transfer Certificate/Record sheet from the last attended
                    school (if applicable).
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    Two passport-sized photographs of the attendants responsible
                    for receiving/visiting the student.
                  </li>
                </ol>
                <br />

