                  All payments are to be made in Indian Rupees only.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  Upon admission, the first installment of tuition fees,
                  admission fee, registration fee, and security deposit must be
                  paid.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  The second installment of tuition fees should be paid on or
                  before 10th November of the academic year.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  Annual charges will be collected at the beginning of the
                  session.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  Payment can be made in cash, Demand Draft, or local cheque,
                  favoring 'EDIFY SCHOOL,' payable at Bengaluru.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  Fees once paid will not be refunded or adjusted under any
                  circumstances.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  In the event of a student's withdrawal from the school in the
                  middle of the term, the fee for the entire term must be paid.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  Additional items such as uniforms, shoes, books, stationery,
                  dining, and transportation will incur extra charges.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  Transportation charges will be based on kilometers for 12
                  months, including GPS charges.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  The security deposit is refundable and will be returned when
                  the child leaves the school.
                </Text>
              </li>
              <li>
                <Text type="base">
                  Annual charges cover Taekwando, HOG Dramatic classes, Aniguru
                  Animation, School Cinema value education, Mindedutainment,
                  Edusports, Edurite, field visits, picnics, Olympiads,
                  Interschool competition entry charges, medical fee, journal,
                  magazines, newsletter, examination fee, maintenance fee, PTA,
                  sports fee, activity fee, assignments, and worksheets, etc.
                </Text>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </Collapsible>
          <Collapsible
            title={"Refundable Cash Deposit"}
            titleClass="font-sans font-bold text-xl max-md:text-lg"
            class="mb-5"
            collapseGroup="collapsible"
            plusButtonClass="w-[35px] h-[35px] ml-1"
          >
            <Text type="base">
              The refundable cash deposit is against damage to, or loss of
              library books, laboratory equipment, computer facilities and other
              equipment or assets of the school. It will be refunded without any
              interest, after adjustment of dues, if any, on completion of the
              child's studies at Ekam School.
            </Text>
          </Collapsible>
        </div>
        <div class="p-3 max-md:p-1"></div>
      </div>

      <Footer />
    </div>

    <a href="tel:7676310000">
      <div class="fixed w-full h-14 bg-green-600 bottom-0 left-0 z-10 hidden max-md:flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-4 h-4">
          <Image src={PhoneWhite} alt="Phone" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
        <Text type="sm">+91 76763 10000</Text>
      </div>
    </a>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .float {
    position: fixed;
    /* background-color:#25d366; */
